      "module_path": "track_resolution",
      "docs": "Application service trait for resolving the active track id from the current git branch. The single shared resolution path (IN-04, D2). CLI drives this as the composition root; tests inject a stub BranchReaderPort. Three methods: resolve_active_track (self-resolve only, no explicit id override), resolve_for_read (READ semantics: explicit id overrides branch, no branch guard), resolve_for_write (WRITE semantics: explicit id must match branch-derived id; fail-closed on mismatch or non-track branch). D7 / CN-02 / CN-03 / AC-18 / AC-19.",
